  "description": "From the manufacturer Flexi Black Design Flexi BLACK DESIGN comes in three bold colours that form a striking contrast with the black housing, as well as a subtle all-black lead set off by a classic silver logo. It can be customised with the Multi Box and LED Lighting System accessories (for size S and up). With its innovative Short-Stop Braking System, it creates a high level of safety and comfort during walks. Flexi retractable leashes never slacken as they are always subject to slight tension. With the help of the integrated braking system, you are always able to guide and command your dog. By pushing the brake button with your thumb and a slight pull on the leash you give your dog short orders or leash him back to you. An additional permanent stop function allows you to fix the flexi leash at a certain length. Retractable lead with chrome snap hook Compact and stylish design Secure and comfortable braking system Available in multiple colours Freedom to Roam Reliable Control Durable Lead Practical Accessories",
